<view class="app-shell launch-shell">
  <view wx:if="{{isCheckingConsent}}" class="section-card loading-state">
    <view class="loading-spinner"></view>
    <text class="loading-title">正在检查启动状态…</text>
    <text class="loading-body">FarmerNote 会先确认你是否已经完成协议同意，再决定是否恢复本地数据。</text>
  </view>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="section-card hero-card launch-hero-card">
      <text class="hero-kicker">首次启动需先完成协议确认</text>
      <text class="hero-title launch-title">继续使用前，请先阅读《隐私政策》和《用户协议》。</text>
      <text class="hero-body launch-body">
        在你明确同意前，小程序不会恢复本地业务状态，也不会触发云端登录、拍照或日历相关能力。
      </text>
    </view>

    <view class="section-card">
      <text class="section-title">你可以先查看完整说明</text>
      <view class="action-row action-row--pair">
        <button class="action-button secondary-button small-button" bindtap="openPrivacy">查看隐私政策</button>
        <button class="action-button ghost-button small-button" bindtap="openTerms">查看用户协议</button>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="section-card">
      <view class="action-row action-row--stack">
        <button class="action-button primary-button" bindtap="handleAccept" loading="{{isSubmitting}}">
          同意并继续
        </button>
        <button class="action-button ghost-button" bindtap="handleDecline" disabled="{{isSubmitting}}">
          不同意并退出
        </button>
      </view>
      <text wx:if="{{startupError}}" class="helper-text">{{startupError}}</text>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
